      <title>朝鲜金正恩指责韩国就洪水问题进行诽谤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/north-korean-leader-accuses-south-korea-of-a-smear-campaign-over-floods-and-hints-at-rejecting-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——朝鲜领导人金正恩指责韩国“垃圾”媒体夸大最近该国西北部洪水造成的死亡人数，玷污了朝鲜的形象，并暗示他将拒绝首尔提供的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/north-korean-leader-accuses-south-korea-of-a-smear-campaign-over-floods-and-hints-at-rejecting-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 03:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DEI 是什么？为什么它会受到攻击？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/what-is-dei-kamala-harris-and-the-controversy-over-diversity-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从副总统卡马拉·哈里斯成为民主党新任美国总统候选人以来，共和党人就将她称为“多元化人才”，暗示她的晋升是因为她种族和性别，而不是她的智力或能力。支持共和党候选人、前总统唐纳德·特朗普的特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克甚至在他的社交网络 X 上分享了一则虚假广告，其中哈里斯的声音被篡改，称她是“多元化人才的终极代表”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/what-is-dei-kamala-harris-and-the-controversy-over-diversity-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 22:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼部署舰艇和战斗机以增强中东存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/pentagon-deploying-ships-fighters-to-add-to-mideast-presence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列面临伊朗报复暗杀哈马斯和真主党领导人的威胁，五角大楼正通过派遣舰艇、战斗机和弹道导弹防御舰来加强其在中东的存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/pentagon-deploying-ships-fighters-to-add-to-mideast-presence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 22:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币高管将于下周与白宫顾问会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/crypto-executives-to-meet-with-white-house-advisers-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加密货币行业高管计划下周与白宫助手和众议员罗卡纳 (Ro Khanna) 会面，讨论对数字资产的担忧，并为下一届政府提出政策变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/crypto-executives-to-meet-with-white-house-advisers-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 21:38:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber 法律总监托尼·韦斯特将休假参与哈里斯竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/uber-legal-chief-tony-west-to-take-leave-for-harris-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步科技公司首席法律官托尼·韦斯特 (Tony West) 是副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 的妹夫，他暂时离开公司，自愿参与哈里斯的总统竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/uber-legal-chief-tony-west-to-take-leave-for-harris-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 21:26:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉选举结果出炉，未来走向何方？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/venezuela-election-where-s-the-country-headed-after-the-contested-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着委内瑞拉从现代史上最严重的经济衰退中复苏，其独裁总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗似乎愿意在新的公开选举中碰碰运气。尽管胜算不大，但可靠的反对派候选人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯 (Edmundo Gonzalez) 被允许参选，因为马杜罗试图让国际社会相信他尊重民主原则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/venezuela-election-where-s-the-country-headed-after-the-contested-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:49:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗指责委内瑞拉反对派策划武装袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府指责反对派伪造选举记录，声称其候选人击败了总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗，并警告称，据称周六将在被禁领导人玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多呼吁和平示威的地方附近发生武装袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部加大力度避免选举混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部正在为 11 月的总统大选做准备，该部正在关注投票权斗争、调查威胁，并准备恢复与社交媒体公司的简报，以遏制错误信息的传播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
